OL,3,C'Not fit for purpose': Regulator
OL,4,Ccriticised for lack of power
OL,6,FIt has caused confusion over what the
OL,7,FGCRA regulates under the island's
OL,8,Fcurrent competition law and how much
OL,9,Fpower the organisation has in its
OL,10,Fremit.
OL,12,FNick Guillemette of the Guernsey Boat
OL,13,FOwners Association (GBOA) says "It's
OL,14,Fnot powerful enough - they should be
OL,15,Fable to intervene and act as an
OL,16,Feconomic regulator for the island.
OL,17,FWe're on our own, we don't have an
OL,18,Fombudsman to turn to.
OL,20,F"Basically, it's not fit for purpose."
