OL,6,FSure-Vodafone Airtel Merger
OL,8,FSure and Airtel-Vodafone announced
OL,9,Fplans to merge in the Channel Islands
OL,10,Fin 2022.
OL,12,FIn 2023, the Jersey Competition
OL,13,FRegulatory Authority (JCRA) said it
OL,14,Fcould not approve plans as the merger
OL,15,Fwould only leave JT and Sure as the
OL,16,Ftwo major mobile networks serving the
OL,17,Fisland.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/11
