OL,3,C'Not fit for purpose': Regulator
OL,4,Ccriticised for lack of power
OL,6,FHowever, following a public
OL,7,Fconsultation, the JCRA approved the
OL,8,Fmerger in August, saying "the outcome
OL,9,Fwill protect consumers and ensure
OL,10,Fhealthy competition" after Sure agreed
OL,11,Fto legally binding promises on tariffs
OL,12,Fand pricing.
OL,14,FOrdinarily, mergers would need
OL,15,Fpermission from the GCRA - however,
OL,16,Fthe island's Economic Development
OL,17,FCommittee put forward proposals for
OL,18,FStates Members to review the plans
OL,19,Finstead.
