OL,6,FElectricity prices
OL,8,FSarah De Carteret is a bar manager in
OL,9,FGuernsey and when electricity prices
OL,10,Frose by 10% in July, she was surprised
OL,11,Fthere was no regulatory input on the
OL,12,Fincrease.
OL,14,FSarah says a regulator overseeing
OL,15,Fthese decisions would "make it fair"
OL,16,Ffor businesses.
OL,18,FShe explains: "They're regulating the
OL,19,Fbuilding trade independently, so why
OL,20,Fcan't they do that on electric?
