OL,6,FThe GCRA explains: "Competition
OL,7,Foversight and utility regulation help
OL,8,Fensure households and businesses get
OL,9,Fvalue for money in a marketplace where
OL,10,Fbetter businesses can thrive, and
OL,11,Fcomplacent businesses cannot take
OL,12,Fadvantage of the absence of choice.
OL,14,F"Guernsey has a small economy and
OL,15,Fsubscale in many sectors, but we want
OL,16,Fthe Guernsey economy to continue to
OL,17,Fgenerate the wealth that supports the
OL,18,Fthings our community cares about.
