OL,7,Freduce the risk of unfairness and
OL,8,Ferosion of trust in markets if they
OL,9,Fwork mainly in the commercial
OL,10,Finterests of a few.
OL,12,F"Competition oversight and utility
OL,13,Fregulation are key to ensuring that is
OL,14,Fless likely to happen."
